     C                     MOVE NGUKE     WGUKE
     C                     MOVE NSEBN     WSEBN
     C                     MOVE NNOKU     WNOKU
     C                     Z-ADDJSURY     NN1GM
     C           NN1GM     DIV  WCD       NN1ND
     C                     EXCPTDT
     C                     END
     C                     END
